This package provides support files for the Monotype Imprint Shadow
font.


Installation:

1.  Purchase and install the pfb file ImpriMTSha.pfb in
    $TEXMFLOCAL/fonts/type1/monotype/imprintmtshadow

2.  Unzip the file imprintmtshadow.tds.zip in $TEXMFLOCAL.  

3.  Add +miih.map to the configuration files of dvips, pdftex and your
    dvi previewer.

4.  Run texhash and updmap



